description.en:
BKS (Barkis) is a public chain token issued based on the Barkis ultra-high-speed distributed business application blockchain system, which serves as a proof of equity for the entire Barkis ecosystem.

The bottom layer of the Barkis public chain provides technical solutions to the pain  points of the industry through technological innovations such as block structure reorganization.

The Barkis public chain adopts a new BFT-POS double-layer consensus mechanism, cross-chain technology and on-chain governance mechanism to reconstruct the industry ecological chain.

Barkis public chain provides a trusted decentralized basic network for distributed business enterprises and organizations to serve better for blockchain + real economy, improve industry efficiency and promote efficient and coordinated development of society.
